        <briefdescription>
<para>This function looks for the device configuration based on the unique device ID. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The table xvisp_ss_ConfigTable[] contains the configuration information for each instance of the device in the system.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>DeviceId</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is the unique device ID of the device being looked up.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>A pointer to the configuration table entry corresponding to the given device ID, or NULL if no match is found.</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
